<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-262] get_slice needs to allow returning all columns</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-262</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Right now get_slice requires you to enter a &apos;large&apos; value, -1 used to indicate &apos;all columns&apos;. We should allow this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12429005">CASSANDRA-262</key>
            <summary>get_slice needs to allow returning all columns</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
